OL,3,CAppeal for 100th birthday cards for
OL,4,CSecond World War veteran
OL,6,FA branch of the Royal Naval
OL,7,FAssociation is appealing for well-
OL,8,Fwishers to send 100th birthday cards
OL,9,Fto a Second World War veteran who
OL,10,Fserved in the Arctic Convoys to make
OL,11,Fhis surprise celebration extra special.
OL,13,FDougie Shelley, who joined the Royal
OL,14,FNavy aged 17, served as a seaman
OL,15,Fgunner and said earlier this year:
OL,16,F"There's not many of us left."
