OL,4,CSecond World War veteran
OL,6,FThe sailor, of Southend in Essex, was
OL,7,Fon a ship in Hong Kong when news came
OL,8,Fthrough of Germany's surrender, and
OL,9,Fsaid in a previous interview that it
OL,10,F"couldn't have been better".
OL,12,F"The war killed so many people it's
OL,13,Funbelievable," he said. "All around,
OL,14,Fthe Americans, Russians, all the
OL,15,FAllies, the same with the Germans.
OL,17,F"But you were doing a job, the same as
OL,18,Fthey had to. It's either kill or be
OL,19,Fkilled.
