OL,4,CSecond World War veteran
OL,6,F"When we heard about victory in
OL,7,FEurope, everybody got together and we
OL,8,Fall had a good old drink up and jolly
OL,9,Fup, and couldn't welcome it much
OL,10,Fbetter."
OL,12,FMr Shelley, who has no known surviving
OL,13,Ffamily, will turn 100 on September 23.
OL,15,FJohn Hawes, chairman of the Southend
OL,16,Fbranch of the Royal Naval Association,
OL,17,Fis appealing for people to send
OL,18,Fbirthday cards for Mr Shelley, which
OL,19,Fwill be collated at the local branch
OL,20,Fand shown to him at a party on the day.
