OL,4,CSecond World War veteran
OL,6,FThe 76-year-old said Mr Shelley was
OL,7,Fthe branch's "last Arctic convoy
OL,8,Fveteran and also he was at D-Day".
OL,10,FMr Shelley's carer Paul Bennett said
OL,11,FMr Shelley was on the HMS Milne on D-
OL,12,FDay "supporting the chaps going off to
OL,13,Fland in craft ashore in Normandy and
OL,14,Fhe was a gunner keeping the skies
OL,15,Fclear of enemy aircraft".
OL,17,FMr Hawes said the veteran had
OL,18,Fpreviously been the local branch's
OL,19,Fchairman, secretary and treasurer but
OL,20,F"as he got older he had to stop some
OL,21,Fof those jobs".
