OL,6,F"He's always been there, he's always
OL,7,Fgot a smile, he always wants to chat,"
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,F"He really deserves something, he has
OL,11,Fbeen one of our founder members way
OL,12,Fback in 1980 I think it was when the
OL,13,Factual club opened.
OL,15,F"He's always been with us on the
OL,16,FRemembrance Sunday in his wheelchair
OL,17,Fand somebody's pushed him up to the
OL,18,Fcenotaph at Southend."
OL,20,FHe is hoping to collate at least 100
OL,21,Fbirthday cards for Mr Shelley.
