OL,6,F"I think he's going to thoroughly
OL,7,Fenjoy it, he really will, he'll be
OL,8,Fover the moon," said Mr Hawes.
OL,10,F"Dougie always likes to let everybody
OL,11,Fknow he's there and this will blow his
OL,12,Fsocks off I think."
OL,14,FMr Hawes, who was a chef and baker on
OL,15,Fthe aircraft carrier HMS Eagle, is to
OL,16,Fmake Mr Shelley's birthday cake ` a
OL,17,FVictoria sandwich.
